283
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:24,540
He must’ve done that for a reason.

284
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:27,180
The Empress Dowager just did what he asked for.

285
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:29,740
Now the rumors

286
00:16:30,060 --> 00:16:31,180
spread wide and wildly.

287
00:16:31,980 --> 00:16:32,860
If people believe

288
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,340
Madam Li was poisoned and murdered by Her Majesty

289
