behind the curtain.

301
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:05,460
All the laws and policies have been

302
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:07,100
implemented around the country.

303
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:09,860
You’ve just obtained the power,

304
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:11,780
if we change all the laws and policies,

305
00:17:12,060 --> 00:17:13,460
what a chaos it will bring?

306
00:17:52,020 --> 00:17:52,660
Drop.

307
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:06,100
Uncle and brothers,

308
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:07,740
