309
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:15,340
I have.

310
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:20,140
I just want to ask you one question,

311
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:23,500
are you really going to

312
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:27,420
