313
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:30,780
You’ve been blinded for years.

314
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:34,060
You still want to

315
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:35,900
take Liu E as your birth mother?

316
00:18:38,860 --> 00:18:40,860
What about the death of your birth mother?

317
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:42,460
She was buried in haste

318
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:44,540
and you don’t even have the time
to call her mother.

319
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:49,580
And now you just let them off

320
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:53,540
and forget about

321
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,340
