324
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:06,580
to prove if my birth mother is Madam Li.

325
00:19:06,780 --> 00:19:07,900
The truth will come.

326
00:19:09,580 --> 00:19:11,060
But are you sure

327
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:13,860
it’s Her Majesty who killed Madam Li

328
00:19:14,580 --> 00:19:15,860
and buried her in haste

329
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:16,940
to cover her sin?

330
00:19:16,980 --> 00:19:18,300
She just didn’t want you

331
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:19,700
to reunite with your birth mother

332
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:20,740
-for fear of... -Okay.

333
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:25,140
This is about the injustice of Madam Li

334
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:26,820
and the morality of Her Majesty.

335
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:30,260
I shall find the truth.

336
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:34,820
If she has committed such a sin,

337
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:36,780
I shall punish her severely.

338
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:40,060
Imperial guards,

339
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,060
siege the Liu Mansion

340
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,060
make sure no one goes in or out.

341
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:54,140
If you’ll be demoted from

342
00:19:54,140 --> 00:19:56,060
the capital again tomorrow,

343
00:19:57,060 --> 00:19:58,300
then today let me treat you with

344
00:19:58,820 --> 00:19:59,740
a nice meal in the Restaurant of Breeze

345
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:01,660
with goats’ milk wine,

346
00:20:02,260 --> 00:20:04,540
roasted river deer, dried meat, fried hare

347
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:06,140
and lamb soup.

348
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:07,700
I must make your trip

349
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:08,980
to the capital worthwhile.

350
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:10,620
I heard

351
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:13,340
Eighth Prince accused you as a traitor in public,

352
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,540
saying that

353
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:16,460
you are the main person who hides the truth.

354
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:19,340
The court is like the weather in Britain,

355
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:20,620
no one can tell.

356
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:23,740
That’s why we must take the chance

357
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,660
to enjoy all the music and wine

358
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:28,220
in this bustling place.

359
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:31,180
Official duties. Move!

360
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:32,310
Hya!

361
00:20:37,317 --> 00:20:38,701
Hya!

362
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:42,740
This is Zhang Maoze who’s always
at His Majesty’s side.

363
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:47,940
Both troops of the Imperial Guards

364
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:48,980
are sent out.

365
00:20:49,620 --> 00:20:50,820
What are they up to?

366
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:54,180
Forget about this.

367
00:20:54,180 --> 00:20:55,180
Let’s drink.

368
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:57,380
But…

369
00:20:59,940 --> 00:21:01,060
Did His Majesty

370
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:03,260
believe in the rumor?

371
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:06,500
No matter what happened,

372
00:21:06,660 --> 00:21:08,740
