373
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:11,260
Today let’s just enjoy all the new dishes

374
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:13,700
in the Restaurant of Breeze.

375
00:21:13,780 --> 00:21:14,660
Come on.

376
00:21:19,540 --> 00:21:21,940
= Liu Mansion =

377
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,180
The imperial guard

378
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:38,460
sieged the Empress Dowager’s house?

379
00:21:43,540 --> 00:21:44,420
No,

380
00:21:49,740 --> 00:21:50,420
it can’t be.

381
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:29,340
= Wang Yaochen, courtesy name Boyong =
I thought I came early,

382
00:22:29,580 --> 00:22:31,380
but I was the late one.

383
00:22:32,900 --> 00:22:34,620
Imperial guards

384
00:22:34,780 --> 00:22:36,620
