388
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,180
Did the rumor turn out to be true?

389
00:22:45,420 --> 00:22:47,060
But if the Family of Liu is punished

390
00:22:47,180 --> 00:22:48,540
soon after Empress Dowager deceased,

391
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:51,980
people would think His Majesty is too cruel.

392
00:22:53,020 --> 00:22:55,100
If there was concrete evidence,

393
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:56,540
they should’ve been taken away.

394
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:58,820
But now they are just sieging the house.

395
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:02,100
If His Majesty wants to figure out the truth,

396
00:23:03,140 --> 00:23:05,180
why does he make such a big deal of it

397
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:07,860
that all the people and officials
are waiting for the result?

398
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:10,020
If the result is the same with the rumor,

399
00:23:10,260 --> 00:23:11,700
the consequences would be unbearable.

400
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:15,660
I still don’t believe in the rumor,

401
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:18,220
but without thorough investigation,
I would always hold doubts.

402
00:23:19,460 --> 00:23:20,580
By doing so,

403
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:25,140
His Majesty showed the justice and
magnanimity of an emperor.

404
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:33,740
After the Empress Dowager deceased,

405
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:36,140
Eighth Prince told me

406
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:40,300
Madam Li

407
00:23:40,980 --> 00:23:42,380
is my birth mother.

408
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:47,220
It is proven to be true
by old concubines and vassals.

409
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:51,140
I feel devastated

410
00:23:52,620 --> 00:23:55,940
and ashamed of not performing my duty as a son.

411
00:23:58,100 --> 00:23:59,380
But few days later,

412
00:24:00,060 --> 00:24:02,100
