414
00:24:05,940 --> 00:24:09,580
saying Madam Li was murdered
and buried in disgrace.

415
00:24:14,100 --> 00:24:15,260
Last night,

416
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:17,380
I’ve asked the Imperial Hospital

417
00:24:17,740 --> 00:24:19,220
if there’s a way to verify

418
00:24:19,260 --> 00:24:21,020
the wildly-spread rumor

419
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:23,700
about the murder with poison.

420
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:25,940
They said

421
00:24:27,460 --> 00:24:29,300
it will require to open the coffin
and examine the body.

422
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:32,980
I’ve been thinking about it the whole night.

423
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,500
This involves who gave birth to me

424
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:37,940
and who raised me.

425
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:39,700
Whoever gets wronged

426
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:42,020
or disgraced

427
00:24:42,580 --> 00:24:44,020
is a humiliation to the royal family.

428
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:47,460
Nothing in the royal family is private.

429
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:49,700
Everything happened in here is concerned
with the whole country.

430
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:54,900
No matter it is a disputed case

431
00:24:55,580 --> 00:24:56,620
or rumor

432
00:24:56,620 --> 00:24:57,900
or misinformation,

433
00:24:58,660 --> 00:24:59,620
the truth will be told today

434
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:02,140
to all of you

435
00:25:03,140 --> 00:25:04,620
and people around the country.

436
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:18,340
Mr. Zhao from the Imperial Hospital

437
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:21,540
is in the Yard of Luck with other five doctors.

438
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:24,700
I’d like to ask all of you to go there with me

439
00:25:25,300 --> 00:25:26,660
to take out my mother’s body

440
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:28,980
and examine her right there.

441
00:25:49,700 --> 00:25:52,100
Uncles, please go inside

442
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,340
with me and doctors

443
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:58,220
to examine my mother and find out

444
00:25:58,660 --> 00:26:00,420
if she was poisoned.

445
00:26:44,780 --> 00:26:45,460
Uncle,

446
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:49,180
please tell all the vassals

447
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:50,340
what we saw

448
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:51,860
after we took

449
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:53,580
the coffin out.

450
00:27:11,300 --> 00:27:13,340
We opened the coffin in the house,

451
00:27:14,820 --> 00:27:15,500
and saw...

452
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:21,340
her in Empress Dowager’s dress.

453
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:24,220
She looked as if she just fell asleep.

454
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:27,420
= Li Yonghe, courtesy name Shenli =
Doctors said

455
00:27:28,780 --> 00:27:31,140
it’s because she’s preserved with mercury.

456
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,900
Her funeral

457
00:27:36,260 --> 00:27:38,300
was treated with the most respect.

458
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:42,180
We’ve reviewed

459
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:44,580
her case report

460
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:47,260
last night,

461
00:27:48,180 --> 00:27:49,900
and didn’t find anything suspicious.

462
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:54,780
Today we opened the coffin and examined carefully.

463
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:58,540
we didn’t find any evidence showing
she had been poisoned.

464
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:01,300
So the rumor

465
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,580
is proved to be wrong.

466
00:28:12,740 --> 00:28:14,700
Now we learned we shouldn’t be fooled by rumors.

467
00:28:16,300 --> 00:28:17,780
even those who is upright

468
00:28:17,780 --> 00:28:18,580
and loyal to the country,

469
00:28:19,180 --> 00:28:20,780
can still be blinded by rumors

470
00:28:21,980 --> 00:28:23,220
if they are biased

471
00:28:24,180 --> 00:28:25,260
and have improper thoughts.

472
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:28,020
Before today,

473
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:30,700
I didn’t reveal the truth sooner,

474
00:28:31,020 --> 00:28:32,820
which caused wildly-spread rumors

475
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:34,340
about Her Majesty

476
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:36,020
in and out of the palace.

477
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,460
It is my fault.

478
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:40,460
Today, the truth is revealed.

479
00:28:41,380 --> 00:28:42,020
From now on,

480
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:45,220
as the officials at the court,

481
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:48,100
