486
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:59,300
What about others?

487
00:29:03,060 --> 00:29:04,900
I feel ashamed of myself.

488
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:27,780
I shall repent of my sins

489
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:30,020
and ask Her Majesty’s forgiveness.

490
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:45,660
Your Majesty,

491
00:29:47,860 --> 00:29:49,500
your story has been told.

492
00:30:14,180 --> 00:30:15,380
The Emperor announced that

493
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:17,740
Her Majesty protected me

494
00:30:18,060 --> 00:30:20,500
for 12 years with due diligence and merits.

495
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:22,860
Yet some insensible people

496
00:30:23,180 --> 00:30:25,220
defamed Her Majesty with rumors

497
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:27,540
which is not what I want as a son.

498
00:30:28,820 --> 00:30:29,580
I told you

499
00:30:29,580 --> 00:30:30,780
the rumor is not true.

500
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:32,260
How can an Empress Dowager

501
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,340
be so malicious?

502
00:30:33,340 --> 00:30:33,900
Right,

503
00:30:34,060 --> 00:30:36,020
Her Majesty followed the late Emperor’s command

504
00:30:36,020 --> 00:30:37,220
to raise His Majesty,

505
00:30:37,220 --> 00:30:39,220
but she also treated Madam Li well.

506
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:41,380
She raised His Majesty for more than 10 years.

507
00:30:41,620 --> 00:30:43,540
She has contributed to the court.

508
00:30:43,540 --> 00:30:44,020
Yes, yes.

509
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,460
His Majesty is kind indeed.

510
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:47,220
A merciful mother and an obedient son

511
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:48,700
won’t be turned against each other.

512
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,660
The Emperor announced that

513
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:53,220
Her Majesty protected me

514
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:55,940
for 12 years with due diligence and merits.

515
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:57,860
The proposal from you

516
00:30:58,100 --> 00:31:00,100
helped His Majesty a lot to make this announcement.

517
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:02,500
You were afraid of Her Majesty
when she’s holding the power,

518
00:31:02,620 --> 00:31:04,940
and you never dropped down a stone on the one

519
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:05,900
