520
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:08,580
You are a real gentleman.

521
00:31:09,140 --> 00:31:10,340
It’s just duty.

522
00:31:15,060 --> 00:31:16,140
But I didn’t expect

523
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:19,660
