524
00:31:20,620 --> 00:31:22,460
That is to keep the loyal and remove the evil.

525
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:24,020
His Majesty is wise.

526
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:27,860
I’m not an idiot.

527
00:31:28,620 --> 00:31:29,620
Back then and now,

528
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:31,460
what you did for Her Majesty

529
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:33,260
is always to consider the interest of the whole.

530
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,700
His Majesty’s birth mother Madam Li

531
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:39,700
earned the title she deserves,

532
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,300
with two Empress Dowagers

533
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:43,140
accompanying the late Emperor,

534
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:46,340
His Majesty should feel relieved.

535
00:31:47,340 --> 00:31:48,780
His Majesty stepped onto the throne
when he was young,

536
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:51,460
and now he finally took the court in his hand,

537
00:31:51,580 --> 00:31:52,820
that is a huge blessing.

538
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:53,900
Now

539
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:56,060
we have loyal officials at the court

540
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,620
