541
00:31:57,900 --> 00:32:00,500
and talents like Yongshu, Zhigui

542
00:32:01,220 --> 00:32:02,460
and Junmo gathered around His Majesty.

543
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:03,420
With their support,

544
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:05,340
they will bring prosperity

545
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:07,020
and peace to the people.

546
00:32:09,100 --> 00:32:11,620
Farewell, Shuyu.

547
00:33:10,140 --> 00:33:10,940
Your Majesty,

548
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:13,740
Consultant Han submitted so many proposals

549
00:33:14,140 --> 00:33:16,820
