and business will be promoted,

557
00:33:38,940 --> 00:33:40,140
and tax revenue will be increased.

558
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:45,420
The Imperial Examination, Tea Tax

559
00:33:45,780 --> 00:33:47,060
Neighborhood, and Western Terrain,

560
